<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <title>
    <%= title %>
  </title>
  <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/style.css' />
</head>

<body>

  <div class="min-h-screen flex flex-col">
    <!--! Header -->
    <header class="bg-white shadow-sm">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-4 flex justify-between items-center">
        <div class="flex items-center space-x-2 ">

          <div class="text-emerald-600">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5"
              stroke="currentColor" class="size-6">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                d="M12 6.042A8.967 8.967 0 0 0 6 3.75c-1.052 0-2.062.18-3 .512v14.25A8.987 8.987 0 0 1 6 18c2.305 0 4.408.867 6 2.292m0-14.25a8.966 8.966 0 0 1 6-2.292c1.052 0 2.062.18 3 .512v14.25A8.987 8.987 0 0 0 18 18a8.967 8.967 0 0 0-6 2.292m0-14.25v14.25" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <span class="font-bold text-xl">Biblio App</span>
        </div>
        <nav class="hidden md:flex space-x-6">
          <a href="#caracteristicas" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-emerald-600 transition-colors text-xl">
            Características
          </a>
          <a href="#acerca" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-emerald-600 transition-colors text-xl">
            Acerca de
          </a>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </header>

    <!--! Hero  -->
    <section class="flex-grow bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-emerald-100 py-16 md:py-24">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
            Gestiona tu colección de libros de forma sencilla y rapida
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8">
            Una aplicación simple pero potente para catalogar, organizar y gestionar todos tus libros en un solo
            lugar.
          </p>          <a href="/auth/login"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-lg font-medium text-white bg-emerald-600 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:bg-emerald-700 transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-emerald-500 focus:ring-offset-2">
            Iniciar Sesión

          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!--! Caracteristicas  -->
    <section id="caracteristicas" class="py-16 bg-white">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Características Principales</h2>
        <!--! Tarjetas -->
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">

          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">

            <div class="flex flex-row items-center mb-4 gap-1.5">
              <div class="bg-emerald-100 w-12 h-12 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-emerald-600">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5"
                  stroke="currentColor" class="size-6">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                    d="M12 21v-8.25M15.75 21v-8.25M8.25 21v-8.25M3 9l9-6 9 6m-1.5 12V10.332A48.36 48.36 0 0 0 12 9.75c-2.551 0-5.056.2-7.5.582V21M3 21h18M12 6.75h.008v.008H12V6.75Z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Organiza tu Biblioteca</h3>
            </div>

            <p class="text-gray-600">Cataloga todos tus libros con detalles como título, autor</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
            <div class="flex flex-row items-center mb-4 gap-1.5">
              <div class="bg-emerald-100 w-12 h-12 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-emerald-600">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5"
                  stroke="currentColor" class="size-6">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                    d="m21 21-5.197-5.197m0 0A7.5 7.5 0 1 0 5.196 5.196a7.5 7.5 0 0 0 10.607 10.607Z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Búsqueda Rápida</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Encuentra cualquier libro en segundos con nuestro potente buscador.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
            <div class="flex flex-row items-center mb-4 gap-1.5">
              <div class="bg-emerald-100 w-12 h-12 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-emerald-600">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5"
                  stroke="currentColor" class="size-6">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                    d="m16.862 4.487 1.687-1.688a1.875 1.875 0 1 1 2.652 2.652L6.832 19.82a4.5 4.5 0 0 1-1.897 1.13l-2.685.8.8-2.685a4.5 4.5 0 0 1 1.13-1.897L16.863 4.487Zm0 0L19.5 7.125" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Edición Sencilla</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Actualiza la información de tus libros con facilidad cuando lo necesites.</p>
          </div>

        </div>

      </div>

    </section>

    <!--! CTA  -->
    <section class="bg-emerald-600 py-16">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">¿Listo para organizar tu colección?</h2>
        <a href="/dashboard"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-lg font-medium text-emerald-600 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-white">
          Comenzar Ahora
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!--! Footer  -->
    <footer id="acerca" class="bg-gray-800 text-white py-8">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center">
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-2 mb-4 md:mb-0">

            <div class="text-emerald-600">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5"
                stroke="currentColor" class="size-6">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                  d="M12 6.042A8.967 8.967 0 0 0 6 3.75c-1.052 0-2.062.18-3 .512v14.25A8.987 8.987 0 0 1 6 18c2.305 0 4.408.867 6 2.292m0-14.25a8.966 8.966 0 0 1 6-2.292c1.052 0 2.062.18 3 .512v14.25A8.987 8.987 0 0 0 18 18a8.967 8.967 0 0 0-6 2.292m0-14.25v14.25" />
              </svg>
            </div>

            <span class="font-bold text-xl">Biblio App</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">
            © Daniel Trejos - 2025. Todos los derechos reservados.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </footer>

  </div>

</body>

</html>